把 `present` 改成 `push` 就行，前提是当前页在 `UINavigationController` 里。

```objc
ServiceViewController *sVC = [[ServiceViewController alloc] init];
[self.navigationController pushViewController:sVC animated:YES];
```

你当前代码位置在 [MyViewController.m](/Users/liuyifu/Documents/work/SpeakEasy/SpeakEasy/Controller/My/MyViewController.m) 的 `didSelectItemAtIndexPath` 里，把这段：

```objc
sVC.modalPresentationStyle = UIModalPresentationFullScreen;
[self presentViewController:sVC animated:YES completion:nil];
```

替换掉即可。

如果 `self.navigationController == nil`（例如当前是 `present` 出来的），就需要先把入口改成用导航控制器承载，或者临时兜底：

```objc
if (self.navigationController) {
    [self.navigationController pushViewController:sVC animated:YES];
} else {
    UINavigationController *nav = [[UINavigationController alloc] initWithRootViewController:sVC];
    nav.modalPresentationStyle = UIModalPresentationFullScreen;
    [self presentViewController:nav animated:YES completion:nil];
}
```

